SIMPLEREGISTRATION_DESCRIPTION=<img src="http://extensions.gibilogic.com/images/gibilogicextensions-150x150.png" alt="" style="float: left;margin: 0 10px 10px 0" /><h1>GiBi Simpleregistration</h1><h2>A Joomla extension by <a href="http://www.gibilogic.com">GiBiLogic</a></h2><p>This component allows user to register by inserting only an e-mail address: it will be used both as "Full name" and "Username"; password will be created randomly and sent to the user.</p><p>To use this component, just create a menu item which links to Simple Registration -> Registration Form.</p><p>Discover other extension by <strong>GiBiLogic</strong> at <a href="http://extensions.gibilogic.com">extensions.gibilogic.com</a></p>
